LDBC Social Network Benchmark — Dataset Attribution
=====================================================

This directory contains data generated by the LDBC Social Network Benchmark
Data Generator (ldbc_snb_datagen), Scale Factor 0.1.

Source: https://ldbcouncil.org/benchmarks/snb/
Download: https://datasets.ldbcouncil.org/snb-interactive-v1/

