  http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0

Modifications to the original data files:
  - CSV column headers containing dots (e.g. "Person.id") were renamed to
    underscore-separated names (e.g. "person_id") for SQL compatibility.
  - Duplicate column headers (e.g. two "Person.id" columns in
    person_knows_person) were renamed to distinct names (e.g. "src", "dst").
  - No data values were modified.
